{"tid":775933,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【嚇親大男人】「救命！有隻BB松鼠追住我」 德男報警 揭松鼠找媽媽","createTime":"2018-08-11T14:30:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T18:12:29.000Z","uid":28765,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1ca18bf547c575576fc1d2c79e523f7e5716d6a3","tid":775933,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T14:30:34.000Z","msg":"「救命，我被隻松鼠BB追！」這並非警方慣常收到的求助電話，但德國警方前日確收到如此一個求助電話，報案人更是一名男子。<br />\n德國卡爾斯魯卮(Karlsruhe)警局周四上午約8時，收到一名男子報案求救，表示自己被一隻小松鼠窮追，警方派員往調查，真的見到該名可憐男子和一隻鍥而不捨的小松鼠。<br />\n警員立刻為松鼠蓋毯保暖，由於牠已筋疲力盡，所以很快便入睡。警方為松鼠起了一個名字 -- 「卡爾-弗里德里希」(Karl-Friedrich)，暫時把牠「拘留」警署內，直至為牠找到新居所。<br />\n警方發言人說，當小松鼠失去母親，通常會纏著一個人希望得到收留，「牠們可以很堅持，不單止追著某人，更是死纏不放」。<br />\n發言人又說，報案男子可能不知如何應對，「他肯定有點受驚」。<br />\n英國《每日郵報》  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180811/large/1533946964_0424.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180811%2Flarge%2F1533946964_0424.jpg&h=8c9ad7c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小松鼠獲警員悉心照顧<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180811/large/1533946963_93de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180811%2Flarge%2F1533946963_93de.jpg&h=f0bc3fc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小松鼠倦極而睡<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180811/large/1533946963_2f65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180811%2Flarge%2F1533946963_2f65.jpg&h=85226fba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小松鼠倦極而睡<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180811/58549806\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180811%2F58549806&d=hyevoFEhWk2UO4wypl802wdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=d733822e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180811%2F58549806&h=19d74cb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180811/58549806</a>"},{"pid":"2c3ba7ef622b2cba20519194dd80559fa0c77a0f","tid":775933,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T14:31:28.000Z","msg":"錯台添<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c653e8caa8b894ef02ce3ef3f702e5dfc29108f","tid":775933,"uid":185165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T16:02:23.000Z","msg":"好cute<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望會收留佢"},{"pid":"1a0c5a9b4b6f848a01a100900157b5677a077b7c","tid":775933,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T18:12:29.000Z","msg":"唔係嚇親，係 animal welfare. <br />\n<br />\n試過有隻貓狂跟我超過兩三條街，唔報唔識搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}